OL,3,CCampaign to save one of Scotland's
OL,4,Coldest churches
OL,6,FPeople in the Scottish Borders are
OL,7,Fcampaigning to save one of Scotland's
OL,8,Foldest christian places of worship.
OL,10,FThe Linton Kirk church sites is almost
OL,11,F900 years old, with records showing
OL,12,Fits first minister was recorded in
OL,13,F1127.
OL,15,FIt is now up for sale, as the Church
OL,16,Fof Scotland looks to sell off a number
OL,17,Fof its buildings across the country
OL,18,Fdue to falling congregation numbers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
