OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773778272
OL,3,CCampaign to save one of Scotland's
OL,4,Coldest churches
OL,6,FThe building can be purchased
OL,7,Fexclusively by the community until mid-
OL,8,FApril. After that, it is set to be
OL,9,Fadvertised publicly for around #35,000.
OL,11,FCampaigners are now fundraising in a
OL,12,Fbid to prevent the site from falling
OL,13,Finto the hands of private owners.
OL,15,FSince the 1980's a community group has
OL,16,Fbeen running to care for and maintain
OL,17,Fthe building, meaning the Linton Kirk
OL,18,FHeritage Appeal could hit the ground
OL,19,Frunning when the Church of Scotland
OL,20,Fcommunicated to them in 2025 that it
OL,21,Fplanned to sell off the building.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773778272
OL,3,CCampaign to save one of Scotland's
OL,4,Coldest churches
OL,6,FSimon Oldham is the treasurer, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "The thought of losing a
OL,8,Fbuilding with the history and sense of
OL,9,Fpeace that Linton Kirk has was quite a
OL,10,Fsad prospect for us and also for many
OL,11,Fof the local community as well."
OL,13,FThe group has fundraised around 25% of
OL,14,Fthe asking price so far - and say they
OL,15,Fare confident they can meet the asking
OL,16,Fprice in time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
