PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773778272
OL,3,CCampaign to save one of Scotland's
OL,4,Coldest churches
OL,6,FThere is a plaque on display in the
OL,7,Fchurch showing the first recorded
OL,8,Fminister of the church was in 1127,
OL,9,Falmost 900 years ago, making Linton
OL,10,FKirk one of the oldest in Scotland.
OL,12,FPeople in the area are passionate
OL,13,Fabout protecting the church.
OL,15,FFormer church elder Margaret McTavish
OL,16,Fsaid: "We were aware of Linton Kirk
OL,17,Fwhen we came here on holiday to stay
OL,18,Fin a little cottage when my family
OL,19,Fwere young. We got very involved in
OL,20,Fcoming to Sunday services, if there
OL,21,Fwas a service on when we came.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773778272
OL,3,CCampaign to save one of Scotland's
OL,4,Coldest churches
OL,6,F"Hundreds, hundreds of people have
OL,7,Fworshipped in this building over all
OL,8,Fthese years. I just thought it was
OL,9,Fshocking it was up for sale."
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Alastair Fleming is the
OL,12,FChair of the Linton Kirk Heritage
OL,13,FAppeal. He added: "The family have
OL,14,Fbeen in the parish for 80 plus years,
OL,15,Fand been heavily involved with the
OL,16,Fchurch, and you felt part of you was
OL,17,Fbeing taken away, hence the appeal and
OL,18,Fthe crowd funding, to try and keep it
OL,19,Fwithin local ownership."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
